---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How AIForEdu.ai collects, uses, and protects your information.">
  <section class="page-hero section-shell-tight">
    <div class="container-full">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="mt-6 page-title">Privacy policy</h1>
        <p class="page-lede">How AIForEdu.ai collects, uses, and protects information related to subscriptions, downloads, and inquiries.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-shell-tight">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="small-note">Last updated: March 1, 2026</p>
      <div class="legal-shell mt-6">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect minimal information necessary to operate AIForEdu.ai. When you subscribe to our newsletter or download a free resource, we collect your email address. When you use our contact form, we collect your name, email, and message. We use Cloudflare Web Analytics, which does not use cookies or track personal data.</p>
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Email addresses are used to send our weekly newsletter (via Beehiiv), deliver requested resources, and respond to inquiries. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties except as needed to operate our services (e.g., our email provider).</p>
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>AIForEdu.ai does not use tracking cookies. We use Cloudflare Web Analytics, which is privacy-first and cookie-free.</p>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use Beehiiv for email delivery, LemonSqueezy for payment processing, and Cloudflare for hosting and analytics. Each service has its own privacy policy.</p>
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Newsletter subscriber data is retained until you unsubscribe. Contact form submissions are retained for 12 months. You can request deletion of your data at any time by emailing hello@aiforedu.ai.</p>
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>AIForEdu.ai is designed for adult education professionals. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.</p>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via our newsletter.</p>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about privacy? Email hello@aiforedu.ai or use our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
